PrecisEnactment of an ORDER PROHIBITING ENTRY ON CERTAIN LANDS IN THE YUKON TERRITORY (1999, No. 2, WHITE RIVER FIRST NATION, Y.T.) - which (a) prohibits staking mineral claims or prospecting for precious minerals on lands which may be required for the settlement of Aboriginal land claims, and (b) repeals the Prohibition Order made by Order in Council P.C. 1999-459.
